room_title: Escape room "R.A.I.N. Corp - Zombie Escape" by Grande Royal Escape in Jacksonville
room_description: Since the 1970's R.A.I.N. CORP. has developed cures and treatments for everything from Ebola to Swine Flu. It's your first day on the job and you are stoked about your position as Lead Security Officer for the facility. You push the mysterious disappearance of the previous Lead Security Officer out of your mind as you prep for the large system of thunderstorms headed your way. You are uncertain why the company has expressed the importance of the power remaining on but with a private power station and a backup generator what could go wrong?
